biotools.summary: IMGT/DomainSuperimpose is the IMGT® tool to superimpose 3D structures of two domains from IMGT/3Dstructure-DB. Domain 3D structures are numbered according to the IMGT-ONTOLOGY concept of IMGT unique numbering.
